fix: show only paternal-line siblings and their descendants

Modified collect() to accept includeSiblings and paternalOnly parameters.
From center person we now show:
- All ancestors (both parents)
- All descendants (all children)
- All siblings
- Paternal-line siblings (father's siblings) and their descendants
- NOT maternal-line siblings (mother's siblings) - reduces line crossings

This matches traditional genealogy tree view following male line for
collateral relatives.
